If there's one thing all true Cincinnatians love, its queen-city style chili. And while there may still be some local dispute as to which chili-chain lays claim to the perfect incarnation, Smithsonian Magazine has officially taken sides. In a list of the 20 Most Iconic Food Destinations of America, 24-hour chili-stop Camp Washington Chili represents some Ohio-Valley flavor. 
